      "text": [
        "3520 - وَ رُوِيَ : فِي اِمْرَأَةٍ قَطَعَتْ ثَدْيَ وَلِيدَتِهَا \"أَنَّهَا حُرَّةٌ لاَ سَبِيلَ لِمَوْلاَتِهَا عَلَيْهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3520 - It is narrated regarding a woman who cut off the breast of her female slave;\n\"She (the slave) is free, and her mistress has no authority over her.\""
        ]
      }
    }
